sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant fe@{ "type": "boundary" } as Admin Panel
    participant API@{ "type": "control" } as API
    participant db@{ "type": "database" } as Database
    participant ms@{ "type": "control" } as Meilisearch

    Note over Admin,ms: Approve OR Reject a PENDING room

    Admin->>+fe: Open pending room list
    fe->>+API: GET /admin/rooms
    API->>API: verifyToken + isAdmin
    API->>+db: room.findMany()
    db-->>-API: All rooms (any status)
    API-->>-fe: 200 data
    fe-->>-Admin: Show rooms with status badges

    Admin->>+fe: Click "Approve" or "Reject" on a room
    alt Approve flow
        fe->>+API: PATCH /admin/rooms/:roomId/approve
        API->>API: verifyToken + isAdmin
        API->>+db: room.findUnique(id, include host)
        db-->>-API: room or null

        alt Room missing
            API-->>fe: 404 "Room not found."
            fe-->>Admin: Show error
        else Room exists
            API->>API: Build updateTasks = [room.update(status=APPROVED)]
            alt Host still has role=USER
                API->>API: Append user.update(role = 'HOST')
            end
            API->>+db: $transaction(updateTasks)
            db-->>-API: All updates committed
            API->>+ms: upsertRoom(room with status=APPROVED)
            ms-->>-API: Indexed (now searchable publicly)
            API-->>fe: 200 "Room approved"
            fe-->>Admin: Refresh list
        end

    else Reject flow
        fe->>+API: PATCH /admin/rooms/:roomId/reject
        API->>API: verifyToken + isAdmin
        API->>+db: room.findUnique(id, include host)
        db-->>-API: room or null

        alt Room missing
            API-->>fe: 404 "Room not found."
            fe-->>Admin: Show error
        else Room exists
            API->>+db: room.update(status=REJECTED)
            db-->>-API: Updated
            API->>+ms: upsertRoom(room with status=REJECTED)
            ms-->>-API: Re-indexed (filtered out of public search)
            API-->>fe: 200 "Room rejected."
            fe-->>Admin: Refresh list
        end
    end

    Note over Admin,ms: Note: rejecting does NOT demote a HOST back to USER.<br/>Promotion happens only on first-approval transition.
